title: Nomeansno - Live at Spaceland LA 2001
description:
For the fans of Nomeansno, please know the band allows taping of concerts and does not mind sharing of any live shows in any file sharing format.  Please visit www.nomeanswhatever.com 

If anyone knows who originally recorded this Spaceland show, please have them get in touch with the website.  (no, you&#039;re not in trouble)

2001 Live at the Spaceland Los Angeles.  Rob was just getting over a flu bug so he didn&#039;t spend the show hopping around and making mistakes (his words, not mine).  This video features pretty good sound and was originally shared between members of an old Nomeansno message board.

Please visit the official Nomeansno website for more information on sharing your Nomeansno bootlegs.
